{"hash":"f20bd106af77ce5fa9a5b037c90446e89888c24e","data":{"post":{"id":"34dcf250c48aa86a3126a746dd1c9cfe","category":"기타","sub_category":"Solution","title":"개발자 로드맵","series_name":"","series_num":0,"content":"<p>꾸준히 업데이트되고 있는 로드맵이다.</p>\n<p>해외 개발자들이 오픈소스로 정리하고 배포하는 프로젝트인데</p>\n<p>한글로 번역된 내용이 있어서 올려본다.</p>\n<p>무조건 정답이라고 할 순 없지만 충분히 도움이 되는 것 같다.</p>\n<p>(다른 파트 로드맵은... 사이트에서)</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"백엔드-개발자\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B1%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>백엔드 개발자</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F3cbda823-4f9f-4d3a-8304-a8d7bfd79a63%2F120199163_197891628366431_5660893118453603052_o.jpg?table=block&#x26;id=31b89e99-f48d-4e15-a2ae-3b2ca06b8043&#x26;width=2950&#x26;userId=038a9d8a-4e75-4deb-a374-ed6ff93980c6&#x26;cache=v2\"></p>\n<hr>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"데브옵스-개발자\"><a href=\"#%EB%8D%B0%EB%B8%8C%EC%98%B5%EC%8A%A4-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>데브옵스 개발자</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F2cdebbc5-36b1-4c1e-8acf-5d1ae87fef69%2F120289515_197891651699762_5766344256591660931_o.jpg?table=block&#x26;id=faf2e525-1382-4990-a8c3-93457e71551e&#x26;width=2950&#x26;userId=038a9d8a-4e75-4deb-a374-ed6ff93980c6&#x26;cache=v2\"></p>\n<hr>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"reference\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Reference</h2>\n<span class=\"reference\">\n<p><a href=\"https://roadmap.sh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Developer Roadmaps</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kamranahmedse/developer-roadmap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/devJang/developer-roadmap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github: Korean</a></p>\n</span>\